Returns the infix representation of the expression.

project_385 - package project_385
 

T

tokenizer(String) - Method in class project_385.Parser
Returns a list of tokens from a given string.
Algorithm: Loop through all characters in the input string. If the character is an operator or a parenthesis, append the character to the token list. Otherwise if the character is a letter, create a string of characters from the current
character to the next non-alphanumeric character
and append that to the token list.
